trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Process.OutputDataReceived"></xref> and <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Process.ErrorDataReceived"></xref> events.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Process.OutputDataReceived"> </xref> og <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Process.ErrorDataReceived"> </xref> hendelser.

trans-unit.source: To asynchronously collect the redirected <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process.StandardOutput%2A> or <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process.StandardError%2A> stream output of a process, you must create a method that handles the redirected stream output events.
trans-unit.target: Asynkront samle inn den omadresserte <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process.StandardOutput%2A>eller <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process.StandardError%2A>dataflyten lagrer for en prosess, må du opprette en metode som håndterer omdirigerte dataflyten utdata hendelser.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Process.StandardError%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Process.StandardOutput%2A>

trans-unit.source: The event-handler method is called when the process writes to the redirected stream.
trans-unit.target: Metoden hendelsesbehandlingen kalles når prosessen skriver til omdirigerte dataflyten.

trans-unit.source: The event delegate calls your event handler with an instance of DataReceivedEventArgs.
trans-unit.target: Representanten hendelsen kaller hendelsesbehandlingen med en forekomst av DataReceivedEventArgs.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.DataReceivedEventArgs.Data%2A> property contains the text line that the process wrote to the redirected stream.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.DataReceivedEventArgs.Data%2A>-egenskapen inneholder tekstlinje prosessen skrevet til omdirigerte dataflyten.</xref:System.Diagnostics.DataReceivedEventArgs.Data%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the line of characters that was written to a redirected <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Process"></xref> output stream.
trans-unit.target: Henter linje med tegn som er skrevet til en omadressert <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Process"> </xref> utdata dataflyten.

trans-unit.source: The line that was written by an associated <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Process"></xref> to its redirected <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process.StandardOutput*> or <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process.StandardError*> stream.
trans-unit.target: Linjen som ble skrevet med en tilknyttet <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Process"> </xref> til den omadresserte <> </> *> eller <> </> *> dataflyten.
